reviewText: I own this dvd and I think it is a great dvd to own if you like and or love Zoboomafoo. Zoboomafoo is my second favorite tv show. I love this dvd because it comes with four different Zoboomafoo eposides.

Zoboomafoo is definitely one of the best children's programs around. It's intelligent, informative and fun for parents as well as kids. This particular zoboo c.d. is my childs favorite. Don't be surprised if the kids want to watch it over and over and over............
